"Nightshift!"

A single voice attempted to penatrate into the fog of unconsciousness.
"Nightshift wake up!" The voice spoke again, it was WOLFGANG's voice
and he was standing over NIGHTSHIFT as they were both on the shuttle
that had brought them into the jungle in the first place.

The shuttle was jostling as if it was in the air and flying in an
erratic pattern, the windows outside the shuttle showing that they
were indeed flying.

"Nightshift wake up!" This time the voice was RAMULUS as he also stood
on another side, a medical kit in his hand, he was adminstering
something to NIGTSHIFT.

(TAG)

Preston
